- `.edit-journal-container .editor-shell` override

All styling now comes from the existing `editor.css` classes.

## Verification
1. Open profile page, click edit on any post (grid or list view)
2. EditJournal should appear as full overlay covering the profile page (with backdrop blur), centered modal card matching the Editor's look
3. Close button, title input, toolbar, editor area, and save button should all match Editor.jsx styling
4. Editing and saving should still work correctly
5. Test on mobile viewport sizes
